targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__time(insight_date),
  media_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY insight_date

select
  	count(media_id)
from
  "Story"
where 
  extract(epoch from timestamp::timestamp) > extract(epoch from now()) - 86400
  and instagram_business_account = $user_id

SELECT
  $__time(insight_date),
  followers_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY insight_date

SELECT
  $__time(insight_date),
  follows_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY insight_date

WITH engTotal as (
select sum(engAll) as eng
from (
	select max(engagement) as engAll
	from "MediaInsights" mi
	where mi.media_id in (select media_id from "Media" order by "timestamp" desc limit 20)
	group by mi.media_id 
	) as engList
)

SELECT
  cast (engTotal.eng as float)*100/20 / followers_count as engRate
FROM "UserInsights", engTotal
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER by insight_date desc
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  followers_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
  and instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  sum(like_count)
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
  and $__timeFilter(timestamp)

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  likes_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
  and instagram_business_account = $user_id

SELECT
  sum(comments_count)
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
  and $__timeFilter(timestamp)

select sum(reqSaved.totalSaved) 
from (select distinct(mi.media_id), max(mi.saved) as totalSaved
from "MediaInsights" mi, "Media" m
where saved is not null and mi.media_id = m.media_id and m.instagram_business_account = $user_id and $__timeFilter(timestamp)
group by mi.media_id) as reqSaved
